%define module_name CGI
Name: perl-CGI
Version: 4.40
Release: alt1

Summary: Simple CGI class for Perl
License: perl
Group: Development/Perl

URL: https://metacpan.org/module/CGI
Source0: http://www.cpan.org/authors/id/L/LE/LEEJO/%{module_name}-%{version}.tar.gz
